1. *Osećaj* da ćeš biti srećan je divna stvar. (The feeling that you will be happy is a wonderful thing.)

2. Ona nikad ne gubi *osećaj* da je pravična. (She never loses her sense of justice.)

3. On ima *osećaj* za humor. (He has a sense of humor.)

4. Ona je imala *osećanje* da će se nešto loše desiti. (She had a feeling that something bad was going to happen.)

5. Ona je imala *osećaj* da će se sve na kraju dobro završiti. (She had a feeling that everything would end well.)

6. On je imao *osećaj* da mu je sve u životu u redu. (He had a feeling that everything was okay in his life.)